name: Herbert Clifford
description: I am a very open minded person, someone who accepts people as they are, I am a fair individual who adapts to changes in life and enjoys life to the fullest.I’m proud of myself in being honest and most trustworthy, I seek that in a mate, someone who is compassionate yet understanding who has a calm behavior and a great personality.I am generally an optimistic person with a good sense of humor, fairly easy-going, and I don’t think that I’m too critical about things, but I also believe that it takes two people contributing to a relationship to make it work.
